</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Quote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">There would be exceptions. There is no way in hell the kinda of disaster created by that Tsunami would fail to elicit humanitarian aid from a libertarian government. Again, I think their grandstanding one-liners are giving people the wrong idea.
