</span><table width="90%" cellspacing="1" cellpadding="3" border="0" align="center"><tr> 	  <td><span class="genmed"><b>Flarestar wrote:</b></span></td>	</tr>	<tr>	  <td class="quote">Stating that the USA has the best universities in the world is also a misconception, as frankly Japan's universities blow ours away.</td>	</tr></table><span class="postbody">
